Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.15,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,超体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.11,0:30:57.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我的腿!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.90,0:48:43.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我接到一个美国公民从台湾打来的奇怪电话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.66,0:48:47.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,一个年轻女子给我们提供了大型贩毒团伙信息
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.39,0:48:49.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,- 我来处理   - 好的 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.10,0:50:08.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.68,0:50:18.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.14,0:50:21.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,德国 柏林
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.46,0:50:22.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.24,0:50:31.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,是他! 抓住他!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.95,0:50:42.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,请跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.95,0:50:54.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,法国 巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.31,0:51:03.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.21,0:51:06.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,先生 跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.33,0:51:18.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,意大利 罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.33,0:51:24.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,欢迎来到罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.06,0:51:33.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,早上好 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:36.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,你好 跟我过来 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.30,0:52:07.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,好的 三个都抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.90,0:55:18.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,她小腹有伤疤?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.65,0:55:20.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,是的 是我们给她取出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.07,0:55:23.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,- 她还好吗?  - 很好 她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.43,0:55:26.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我给她注射了一针 她一天内会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.49,0:56:11.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,- 医生 她醒了  - 你确定?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.45,0:56:12.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,是的 她坐在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.88,0:56:18.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.94,0:56:21.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,- 你没铐住她?  - 必须有啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.34,0:57:22.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,别把车放那里 停好了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.83,0:58:54.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,伙计们 进去!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.24,0:59:03.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,和警察说去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.15,0:59:08.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我看着手术
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.65,0:59:11.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,- 去弄点吃的来  - 你这个吃货
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.02,1:02:18.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,嘿 我给你买了...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.40,1:03:01.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,杀了她 拿到毒品
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.83,1:03:20.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,别傻站着 杀了她!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.73,1:05:37.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,跟上那辆车
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.55,1:07:28.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,老大 我们有五个人死在医院 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.90,1:07:31.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,还剩多少人手?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.75,1:07:34.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我这边还有二十五人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.55,1:07:37.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,该死的 她真顽强 她是个巫婆
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.98,1:07:42.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.74,1:07:46.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我要亲手杀了她
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.02,1:10:08.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,给我搜整个大楼 找到她!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.06,1:13:53.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,冲俊!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.03,1:13:55.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我在这里 老大!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.73,1:13:57.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.46,1:13:59.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,好的 老大!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.70,1:14:02.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,你们 给我上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.41,1:14:04.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.48,1:14:07.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.80,1:14:11.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,快找医生 快!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.47,1:20:53.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,她呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.89,1:20:59.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,她人呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.74,1:21:00.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.71,1:21:03.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:02.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,我无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,十亿年前 我们被赐予了生命\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Life was given to us a billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们用它做了什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What have we done with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就小事一桩 进去就出来 一切都准备就绪了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's as easy as pie. In and out, all done and dusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不自己去办?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Then why don't do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:21.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙绝对想不到会有个大美女来给他送手提箱\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The last thing the guy is expecting is a total 10 turning up to deliver the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你会让他大吃一惊的 来吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll blow his mind. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这里面是什么东西?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,小甜心...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sweetheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,别疑神疑鬼的好吗? 你相信我 不是吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't get paranoid on me, alright? You trust me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德 我是很喜欢你 可是...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Richard, I really do like you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在得先照顾好自己 我有个...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've to take care of myself right now, I got a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 我有好多事得操心\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know, I gotta concentrate on so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿! 嘿! 你上哪去?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey! Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我回家啊 星期一我有考试\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm going home because I have exams on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我得洗个澡 还得复习 好吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I have to shower and I have to study, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:00.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗? 前几天我在博物馆里的时候学到了什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know what? The other day I was in this museum and you know what I found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.81,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,世上第一个女人的名字就叫露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The first ever woman was named Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这能让我心情好一点吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Is that suppose to make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是  - 我会联络你的 好吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- No.  - I'll call you, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,行! 行! 行!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK! OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说实话吧 我没法亲自送箱子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll be honest with you. I can't deliver the case myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我和这家伙之前谈崩了 不是什么大事...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've a little falling out with the guy. It's nothing major...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是你送的话 问题就解决了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but if it's you, problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你走进去 到前台\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You walk in there, you go up to the reception,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,让他叫张先生下来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}you ask Mr. Jang to come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:33.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他下来 拿走手提箱 你给他闪个你最迷人的笑容 然后走人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He comes down, he takes the case, you flash him your prettiest smile and bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 前台从这里都能看得见\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look, you can even see the reception from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 箱子里到底是什么?  - 不知道 就一堆文件\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What's in the case?  - I don't know, it's just some paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是吗? 那让咱看看  - 锁着呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Yeah? Let's see it then.  - It's locked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,除了张先生以外没人有密码\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and no one but Mr. Jang has the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是个送信人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm just the delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这么做有钱赚吗?  - 啊 算是吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Do you get paid to do this?  - Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,大概给多少?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Like how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是在谈价钱了还是...?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK, we're negotiating now or ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是 你能赚多钱? 我想知道 多少?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, no, how much do you get paid? I want to know, how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一千美元\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}A thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,给你一千美金让你送点文件 真的假的?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You get paid a thousand dollars for delivering paperwork, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:10.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 总之只用我十分钟 他们就付我一千块 剩下的不关我的事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know, it takes me 10 minutes and they're paying a grand and the rest is none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 也不关我什么事 我跟你说...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Well, it's not my business either. I'll tell you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听我说!  - 干嘛?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Listen!  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们五五平分\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We split it down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你五百 我五百\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's 500 for you and 500 for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:23.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 理查德 我会打电话给你的  - 听我说! 这礼拜我已经三次\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Richard, I will call you.  - Listen! It is the third time this week
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,出现在同一个酒店 戴着同一顶牛仔帽\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm showing up at the same hotel with the same cowboy hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,问题解决啦\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去吧! 去吧! 我会等着你的  - 露西 宝贝\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Go! Go! I'll wait for you to go.  - Lucy, honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 这活我已经做过十几次了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I... I've done this a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,只是文件! 可能就是他们为了仿造而偷来的一些设计图\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's paperwork! It's probably just some designs they swept so they can copy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这国家就是这样\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's how it works in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就连我的斯泰森牛仔帽也是从这产的 你看!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Even my Stetson was made here. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,标签上写着呢: "台湾制造"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It says so on the label: "Made in Taiwan"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,再会了 戴着冒牌斯泰森牛仔帽的牛仔\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So long, cowboy, with a fake Stetson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 求你了!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Baby, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.81,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德 我得走了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Richard, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干嘛呢?  - 很抱歉\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What the hell are you doing?  - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你到底干...  - 非常抱歉 我是真的需要你的帮助\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What the hell are you do...  - I'm so sorry. I really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,打住! 打住! 马上给我摘下来!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Stop it! Stop it! Take this off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没办法!  - 马上给我摘下来!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I can't!  - Take this off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没办法! 张先生是唯一有钥匙的人!  - 不行!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I can't! Mr. Jang is the only one who has the key!  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要走进酒店里面 跟前台说你要找他\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}All you have to is go into the hotel and ask for him at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 马上给我摘下来!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No! Take it off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起 我真的别无选择 你越快进去就越快出来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm so sorry, I really have no choice. The sooner you go in, the sooner you'll be back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不敢相信你会这么对我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can't believe you did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在这一动不动 我向你保证  - 你的保证连个屁都不值!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I'll be right here, you have my word.  - Your word isn't worth shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,呃... 值五百块 提前支付\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Uh... it's worth 500 bucks, upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个王八蛋!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是棒极了 对不?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And you're wonderful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我能为你效劳吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要找 呃...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm here for, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说是谁要找他?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who should I say is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:01.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,呃... 不对... 理查德叫我... 理查德叫我来的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Uhm... no... Richard sent... Richard sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是理查德\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:18.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德... 呃... 他在找停车位\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Richard's... uh... he's just looking for a place to park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生还是想知道你的名字\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang still wants to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Lucy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:38.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就是露西 他要是能... 要是能快点的话 因为我得... 我得...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just Lucy. If he could... If he could he quick 'cause I have... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,先等我翻译一下...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just a second while I translate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生马上下来 待在这别动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang is on his way, stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我能坐下吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Can I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:56.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生让你待在这别动 我觉得你最好待在这别动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang said you need to stay right here. I think it's better if you stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 皇家酒店\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Excuse me. Regent Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 等等! 不要啊!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, wait! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我什么都不知道!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Wait, I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道! 求求你! 求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know anything! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.21,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,您会说英语吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.28,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会说一点西班牙语\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tambien hablo poco Espanol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西 对 我是露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Lucy, yes, I'm Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.79,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是天大的误解 我只是来送这个手提箱的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's just been a terrible mistake. I'm just suppose to deliver this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:41.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,您钥匙要是丢了 不需要切我的手 切锁链就行 好吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you lost the key, you don't have to chop off my hand, you can just cut the chain, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我求您了 拜托了!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm begging you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要! 不要! 不要呀!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不要! 不要! 求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No! No! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐您好 我会说英语 我为张先生做翻译\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hello, Miss, I speak English. I translate for Mr. Jang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:31.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,请你告诉他 我什么都没做 我什么都不知道\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please tell him that I haven't done anything. I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这整个就是个天大的误解 好吗? 请你跟他说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's all just a big mistake, OK? Please, please tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以 稍等\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, OK, OK, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生想知道箱子里装的是什么\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang wants to know what's in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道里面是什么 你到底会不会说英语?!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Well, I don't know what's in the case. Do you speak English or don't you speak English?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:56.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我会! 我在纽约的一所国际高中里读过一年书\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, I do! I studied one year at International High School in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:03.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德让我把这个箱子给你 我只知道这些\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Richard gave me the case to give to you, that's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好 请你告诉他\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK, please tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他给了我一张写了数字的纸 我不... 这是什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He gave me a paper with numbers written on it, I don't... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是开箱的密码\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's the code to open the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这里面究竟是什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不是危险的东西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nothing dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那他怎么不自己开?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So why won't he open it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他不信任理查德先生\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He doesn't trust Mr. Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.29,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不信任理查德\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't trust Richard either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我只和他谈了一星期的恋爱\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I only dated him for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,行! 行! 行!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK! OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 张先生执意要你打开箱子  - 行! 行!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Mr. Jang insists that you open the case.  - OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 救救我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please God, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他让你利索点 张先生还有要事缠身\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He wants you to hurry up, Mr. Jang has other things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以描述一下箱子里的东西?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Can you describe the content of the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是四个塑料袋 里面装着蓝色的粉末像是...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's 4 plastic pouches filled with blue powder like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是紫色的粉末? 我不知道 看起来挺恶心\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}or maybe a purple powder? I don't know, it looks gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,张先生想给你一份工作\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Jang wants to offer you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,工作?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要工作!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't want a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,生命起源于大约十亿年前\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If life starts approximately a billion years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得在四十万年后\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}we'll have to wait 400,000 years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,才能看到第一波神经细胞演变出来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}to see the aberration of the first nerve cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们说的生命的起点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is where life we know it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,从这些只有几毫米长的脑组织中\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Brains in formation of only a few milligrams
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:09.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法断定 是否有智慧的存在\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}is not possible to determine any sign of intelligence yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,它表现得更像反射作用\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It acts more as a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:17.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一颗脑细胞 你活着 两颗脑细胞 你动着\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}One neuron, you're alive. Two neurons, you're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,而一旦有了活动 就会出现有趣的事情\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And with movement, interesting things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,数百万年前地球上就出现了动物\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Animal life on Earth goes back millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:36.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 大多数物种只使用了大脑的百分之三到五\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yet, most species only use 3-5% of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:40.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有成为人类 达食物链顶端的时候\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But it isn't until we reached human beings at the top of the animal chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才终于发现一种物种更多地使用了其脑容量\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}that we finally see a species used more of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,百分之十看似不多 但要是从人类用它所做的一切来看 已经很多了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}10% may not seem like much but it's a lot if we look at all we've done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们来谈论一个特例\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now let's discuss a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一种比我们更好地利用大脑的生物...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The only living being that uses its brain better than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,据估计 这种不可思议的动物\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's estimated that this incredible animal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用到大脑的百分之二十\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}uses up to 20% of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:52.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其在于 这使它拥有着一种回声定位系统\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And in particular, this allows it to have an echo-location system
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:57.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人类所发明的声纳系统都更加有效\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}that's more efficient than any sonar invented by mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:01.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但是海豚并没有发明声纳 它是自然形成的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But the dolphin did not invent the sonar. It developed it naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:06.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,而这就是我们今天的哲学探讨中\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And this is the crucial part of our
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,最具有关键性的环节\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}philosophical reflection we have today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是否能够得出这样的结论\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Can we therefore conclude
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,即人类更在意\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}that humans are concerned more with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,"拥有"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}"having"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是"具有"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}than "being".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你对我的腹部做了些什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What did you do with my stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么! 只是一个小小的水平切口 刀工非常利落\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nothing! Just a little horizontal slit. It's very well done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一个月之后你会看到 疤痕基本就消失了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and you'll find that in a month, this scar is practically invisible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,明年夏天你就能去海滩秀你的小蛮腰了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll be able to show your tummy off on the beach next summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎有没有疤\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't care about the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 呃... 是不是我们为什么给你开刀?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Is it, uh... is it why we opened you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心 我们没有取你的器官什么的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Rest assured, we didn't harvest your organs or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在你小腹里面放了个小包裹\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Uh, we merely slipped a little package in your lower tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,它是... 一种新毒品 欧洲的孩子们会爱上它的 相信我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's a... it's a new drug the kids in Europe are gonna love, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:57.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 到底是什么?  - 学名叫做CPH4\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What is it?  - Well, the scientific term is CPH4,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,从销售方面来看名字的确不是很诱人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}which is not very sexy from a sale's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呃... 我们... 我们还在想时髦一点的名字...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, uh... we're... we're still working on something a little bit more pop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有建议?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Any suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 请进 很好 哎呦...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Welcome, come on in. Lovely, oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,很不错! 很不错!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Splendid! Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议! 很好很好!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Marvelous! Lovely lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗?  - 我很好 亲爱的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- How are you?  - Very good, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:33.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 呃... 首先 非常感谢各位参与此次的计划\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Right, uh... first of all, many thanks for taking part in this enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信一定会完美完成任务\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}which I'm sure will go off flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这些护照和机票呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}These lovely passport and tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可以让你在接下来的二十四小时内重返家园\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}will enable you to return home in the next 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 当你到达的时候 会有我们的人接应你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, upon arrival, you'll be taken in hand by our people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们才可以收回我们的货\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}so that we might recover our merchandise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.81,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,而你们则可以重新获得那千辛万苦挣来的自由\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and you might re-discover the freedom which you so richly deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,相信你们无需提醒 不过你们之中那些试图\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm sure I don't need to remind you but, for any of those who may be tempted to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:02.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,警告或者把自己交给警方的人呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}warn or turn themselves in to the authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:09.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们手上有你所有家属的姓名和住址 包括你的三姑六婆八大爷\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}we have the names and addresses of the families of every one of you down to the distant cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:15.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们相信你们会慎重行事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, we rely therefore, on your complete discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那么 呃...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Good, anyway, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:22.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们 和女士 请让我作为第一个祝福你们的人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}gentleman, madam, allow me to be the first to wish you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要卖这东西?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You gonna sell this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这就是我们的商业模式\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm afraid it's our business model.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:44.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们这种原始生物来说 生命似乎只有一个目的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}For primitive beings like us, life seems to only have one single purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,获得时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Gaining time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,而花费时间 似乎也正是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And its going through time, seems to be also the only
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们体内每个细胞的真正和唯一的目的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}real purpose of each of the cell in our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,为了达到这个目标 那堆\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To achieve that aim, the mass of the cells
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:22:00.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,能组成包括蚯蚓和人类的细胞\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}that make up earthworm and human beings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,只有两种方法\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}has only 2 solutions:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}be immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:06.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,或是繁衍后代\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}or to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:11.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,若它们的栖息之地不适合繁殖后代\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If its habitat is not sufficiently favourable or nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.15,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,细胞则会选择长生不老\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the cell will choose immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:25.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 自给自足以及自主管理\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}In other words, self-sufficiency and self-management.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 若栖息之地及其有利\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}On the other hand, if the habitat is favourable,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,它们会选择繁殖\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}they will choose to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:48.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 它们死的时候\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That way, when they die,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,会传递必要的信息和知识给下一个细胞\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}they hand down essential information and knowledge to the next cell
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:54.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再传递给下一个细胞 以此类推\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}which hands it down to the next cell and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 知识和学问\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thus, knowledge and learning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,都是通过时间而传承的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}are handed down through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:15.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 保持冷静...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK, OK, keep calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须等待 拖延时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You have to wait, just play for time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:20.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,在飞机上你会有时间想办法的... 先上飞机\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll have time to think it through on the plane... just take the flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:22.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,先上飞机 离开这里\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}take the flight, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最主要的 争取时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's the main thing right now, just save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:28.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别干 保持冷静 你还活着...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't try anything, keep your cool, you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:31.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着... 你还活着 只有这是重要的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}you're alive... you're alive, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,等待 争取时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just wait, save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,争取时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:10.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,老娘我没心情\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们稍微设想一下\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let's imagine for a few moments
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:13.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以启用我们大脑的百分之二十的话\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}what our life would be like if we could access, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:17.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生命会是什么样子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}20 % of our brains' capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:22.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这第一阶段会使我们能够了解并控制\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}This first stage would give us access to and control
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.11,0:26:23.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的身体\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}of our own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.90,0:26:25.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 先生  - 请说?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Sir.  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.22,0:26:27.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这被科学证实了吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Has it been proven scientifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.85,0:26:31.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 目前来说 我承认这只是假设\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, for the moment, it's just hypothesis, I confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:33.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你想想看\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.83,0:26:38.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,早在显微镜被发明几百年前 古埃及人 古希腊人和古印度人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}it's troubling to realize that the Greeks, the Egyptians and the Indians
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:43.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就意识到了"细胞"的存在 这是个让人不安的事实\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}had notion of "cells" centuries before the invention of the microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:45.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,再看看达尔文\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And what to say about Darwin
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:49.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,当他提出进化论的时候 他遭到了所有人的嘲笑\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}whom everybody took for a fool when he put forward his Theory of Evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.66,0:26:52.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,如今需要我们来有所突破\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's up to us to push the rules and laws
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:56.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,从"进化"走向"革命"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and go from "evolution" to "revolution".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:01.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,平均每人有一千亿个神经元\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}100 billion neurons per human,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.44,0:27:04.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,其中被运用的只有15%\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}of which only 15% are activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:09.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,人体内各部分之间的联系比银河中的恒星还要多\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}There're more connections in the human body than there're stars in the galaxy.
