Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.33,0:27:50.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人能使用其大脑百分之百的能力\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But what would happen if for some reason we ignore
