Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:58.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.55,0:28:03.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知道\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've no idea.
