Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.27,0:30:52.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你会说英语吗?  - 会 会\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- You speak English? - Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:54.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 马上送我去医院  - 医院?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Take me to the hospital now.  - Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.57,0:31:45.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 医院  - 在这等我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Hospital.  - Wait for me.
