Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:40.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助 很紧急\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I need help, it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.24,0:32:42.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进来 我们在做手术\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You cannot be in here. We're operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,请你出去!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please, get out!
