Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.78,0:33:23.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我先给你局部麻醉...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Right. I'll just administer local anaethestic...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.20,0:33:24.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:27.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我.... 好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Right, I... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.33,0:33:32.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下 把枪放下来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Calm down, please. Put the gun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.40,0:33:35.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我先... 检查一下 好吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm just going to... examine, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.03,0:33:41.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 介意我用一下吗?  - 不介意\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Do you mind?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.09,0:33:51.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好?  - 妈?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Hello?  - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.95,0:33:54.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.26,0:33:56.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 你打电话来我真开心\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Baby, it's great to hear from you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.66,0:33:58.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你那里现在是几点?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but what time is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.62,0:34:01.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 是晚上了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know. It's night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 先让我把另一通电话挂了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hold on a sec', let me get rid of the other line.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:07.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开始取了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm going to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.12,0:34:09.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 你没有成天出去聚会吧?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm back, you're not partying too much, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.86,0:34:12.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过我会照顾好自己\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You promised me you'll look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.77,0:34:15.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力 妈妈 我努力\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm trying to, Mommy, I'm trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:19.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 谢谢你能意外地打电话回来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Well, thanks for calling out of the blue like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.81,0:34:21.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲错过了你的电话 肯定很难过\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Your father is gonna be sad he missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:26.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他去了健身房还没回来 你一般都是早上打给我们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He isn't home from the gym yet. Usually you call us in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:28.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妈...  - 嗯?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Mom...  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:30.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到了一切\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I feel everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:32.98,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 亲爱的?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What do you mean, sweatie?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.28,0:34:37.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,空间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Space,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,空气\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.33,0:34:45.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,振动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the vibrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:48.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,还有人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.50,0:34:52.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到重力\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can feel the gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.33,0:34:56.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到地球的转动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can feel the rotation of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.77,0:35:00.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,身体的热量在消失\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The heat leaving my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.19,0:35:04.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,血管里的血液在流动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the blood in my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:07.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感受到我的大脑\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can feel my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.50,0:35:11.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我记忆的最深处\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The deepest parts of my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:16.21,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 信号不好 我听不太清你在说什么\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sweatie, we've a bad connection, I can't hear you so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.25,0:35:18.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你说"记忆"怎么了?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What did you say about "memory"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:24.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,当我带上牙箍时 嘴里的疼痛 我...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The pain in my mouth, when I had braces, I ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.77,0:35:30.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我记起我发烧时 你手摸我额头的感觉\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can remember the feeling of your hand on my forehead when I ran a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.22,0:35:34.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得摸到猫的感觉 它真的很软\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I remember stroking the cat. It was so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.31,0:35:37.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,猫? 什么猫 宝贝?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}A cat? What cat, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.87,0:35:40.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝眼睛 断了尾巴的那只暹罗猫\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Siamese with blue eye and a broken tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.77,0:35:43.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你不可能还记得啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sweatie, you can't possibly remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:45.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你那时候只有一岁大\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You were barely a year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:52.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得吃奶的日子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I remember the days of your milk in my mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.43,0:35:54.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.80,0:35:57.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,乳汁...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the liquid...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.73,0:36:03.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你在说些什么啊?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sweatie, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.15,0:36:08.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你我爱你们 爸妈...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I just wanna tell you that I love you, Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:10.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sweatie...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:13.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我想谢谢你们 因为...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And I wanna thank you for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.16,0:36:17.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你们无数次吻在我脸上的感觉我仍感受得到...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}thousand kisses that I can still feel on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:22.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 妈\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I love you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.23,0:36:24.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你 亲爱的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I love you too, sweatie,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,胜过世间任何东西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}more than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.98,0:36:37.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩多少?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}How much is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:40.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,五百克?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}500 grams?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.99,0:36:44.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我身体还需要多少时间把其余的代谢掉?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And how long will it take for my body to eliminate the rest of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.11,0:36:50.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,要回答这个问题 我得知道这是什么\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To answer that, I need to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.39,0:36:51.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:52.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.69,0:36:55.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是CPH4\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}CPH4.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:06.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,孕妇会在怀孕第六周的时候\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Pregnant women manufacture CPH4 in the sixth week of pregnancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.79,0:37:09.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,分泌微量的CPH4\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}in tiny quantities.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.41,0:37:14.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这给婴儿带来了相当于一颗原子弹的能量\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}For a baby, it packs the power of an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:19.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这是胎儿生成骨骼结构所必需的能量\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's what gives the foetus the necessary energy to form all the bones in its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:22.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有人试图人工合成\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've heard they tried to make a synthetic version of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:25.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他们成功了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Didn't realize that they succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:28.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这真是CPH4\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If it really is CPH4,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.40,0:37:31.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,以这个量来说 我真惊讶你竟然还活着\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}in this quantity, I'm amazed you're still alive.
