Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.88,0:46:07.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,细胞核的无限容量\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the infinite capacity of the cell's nucleus,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.16,0:46:11.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,它们都涌向我的大脑 所有的知识...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}they're all exploding inside my brain, all these knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.33,0:46:14.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know what to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.73,0:46:19.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是在问我... 该怎么做...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you're asking me... what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.97,0:46:30.28,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.93,0:46:34.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你想想看\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you think about
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.44,0:46:37.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的本源...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the very nature of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.31,0:46:41.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 生命的最初...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean, from the very begining...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.40,0:46:48.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个细胞的生长... 分裂成两个细胞\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}The development of the first cell... divided into two cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.02,0:46:52.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的全部意义在于\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}This whole purpose of life has been
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:57.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,传承已有的知识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}passed on what was learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.63,0:47:01.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没有更崇高的意义了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's no higher purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:06.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你问我对于你这些正在不断增长的知识 你应该怎么做 我会说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So if you're asking me what to do with all these knowledge you're accumalating, I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.55,0:47:10.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,将它延续下去\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.10,0:47:16.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就像任何一个简单的细胞一样\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just like any simple cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.91,0:47:18.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,通过时间传承\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}going through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.88,0:47:21.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,时间?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.52,0:47:23.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 当然\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.74,0:47:28.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在十二小时之内到你那里\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll be at your door in 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.37,0:47:39.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要走了?   - 是的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- You leaving?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.16,0:47:44.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么?  - 一个处方\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What is this?  - A prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.93,0:47:47.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候开始会写中文了?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Since when did you start writing Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.26,0:47:50.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一小时前  - 露西 我一个字都看不懂\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Since an hour ago.  - Lucy, I don't understand any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:54.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你的肾功能不太好 你的肝脏功能也在减弱 你得改变你的生活方式\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Your kidneys aren't functioning efficiently. Your liver is failing. You need to make some lifestyle changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.83,0:47:57.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,吃这个药 多锻炼 吃些有机食物\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Take this medication. Work out. Eat organic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.77,0:47:59.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你就没问题了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.63,0:48:09.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚十一点 一名女子枪杀了一位病人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Last night, at 11 p.m., a woman shot a patient dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.93,0:48:40.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我是德·里奥\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Del Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:52.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好?  - 我有关于大型贩毒团伙的重要信息\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Hello ?  - Yes, I've important imformation about a group of drug traffickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.83,0:48:55.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟当局说话\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I need to speak with someone in position of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.29,0:49:00.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈 你很幸运 这办公室里没人职位比我高了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ah-hah, you're very lucky. There's no one with more authority in this office than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.06,0:49:02.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,从头开始吧 你叫什么名字?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But let's start with the begining. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.25,0:49:06.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 皮埃尔·德·里奥 离开桌子 坐回椅子上\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Listen up, Pierre Del Rio, get off your desk, sit in your chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.11,0:49:09.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,拿起你左手边的红色笔 记下我要说的每个字\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}pick up the red pen to your left and take down everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.55,0:49:18.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没有摄像头 快点 我没时间浪费了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}There're no cameras, hurry up. I've no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.94,0:49:27.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.97,0:49:31.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,有三个人即将抵达欧洲 我要告诉你他们的详细信息\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm gonna be sending you details of three people about to arrive in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:35.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他们每人都携带了一千克毒品 我要你逮捕他们 拿到毒品\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Each one is carrying a kilo of drugs. I need you to arrest them and collect the substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.46,0:49:36.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍后有用\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:39.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的毒品? 条状? 还是装在胶囊里?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What form of these drugs in? Bars? Capsules?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.68,0:49:43.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,粉末 用塑料袋装着 藏在他们腹内\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Powder, hidden in plastic pouches inside their intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.66,0:49:44.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.66,0:49:47.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,取走的时候一定要小心 那粉末威力很大\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Make sure to be careful when you remove them. The product is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.52,0:49:55.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.19,0:49:58.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.70,0:49:59.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.11,0:50:01.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:03.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我可指望你了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.31,0:51:37.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 没问题\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.18,0:51:56.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我是德·里奥\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Del Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.46,0:51:58.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你回电话给我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks for calling me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.95,0:52:00.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们抓到第三个人了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We got the third guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.33,0:52:03.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 我把交接犯罪分子文件发给你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks very much. I'll send you the paper work with the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.48,0:52:05.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.75,0:52:16.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们 先生们 飞机即将降落于巴黎戴高乐机场\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ladies and gentlemen, we're now beginning our descend to Paris-Charles de Gaulle.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.77,0:52:27.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 现在需要请您关闭电脑\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, I've to ask you to put away your computer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.35,0:52:29.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你该擦擦鼻子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You should wipe your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.21,0:52:31.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?  - 可以给我一杯香槟吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Excuse me?  - May I have a glass of champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.44,0:52:34.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的 当然\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Um, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.86,0:52:55.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 您的香槟\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, your champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.13,0:52:58.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.76,0:53:02.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打扰... 但是 你必须收起小桌板了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm very sorry but... uh, you really need to close your table now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.04,0:53:04.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.07,0:53:15.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,敬知识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.53,0:53:29.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,若它们的栖息之地不适合繁殖后代...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}If the habitat is not sufficiently favorable or nurturing...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:41.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,细胞会选择长生不老\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the cell will choose immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.03,0:53:50.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话来说 自给自足以及自主管理\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}In another word, self-sufficiency and self-management.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.59,0:54:08.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不 女士 女士\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, miss, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.05,0:54:11.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,您必须回到座椅上\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You must remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:13.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 站住!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.20,0:54:19.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.55,0:54:24.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 打开门! 您必须回到您的座椅上! 女士!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, open the door! You really have to go back to your seat! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.93,0:54:26.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上要降落了 请您开门!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're going to land soon, please, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.71,0:54:30.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊 您还好吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Please, say something, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.88,0:54:31.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.04,0:54:34.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.43,0:54:38.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 请开门!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:44.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,快帮忙 帮我打开!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do something, help me open!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.85,0:54:56.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我! 开门!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Answer me! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.51,0:55:09.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士? 您还好吗? 说句话啊!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss? Are you okay? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.40,0:56:24.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 不要动!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Miss, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.06,0:56:28.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要跟你单独谈谈  - 我要你举起双手\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I need to talk to you alone.  - And I need you to put your hands up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.96,0:56:51.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到那几袋东西了吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Did you get the packets?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.22,0:56:54.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.04,0:56:57.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 在哪里?  - 一个安全的地方\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Where're they?  - They're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.23,0:57:00.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就在巴黎\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Here, in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.54,0:57:02.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我更安全\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}They'll be safer in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:33.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 作为警察 怪事我见过一些\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know, as a cop, we see some pretty weird shit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.49,0:57:36.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可是坦白地说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but I've to be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.27,0:57:38.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚在那的举动 把我吓坏了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What you did back there, that freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.47,0:57:41.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,让所有人一下昏睡过去\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To put everyone to sleep like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.72,0:57:43.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我该担心吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}do I need to be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.04,0:57:45.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不用\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.51,0:57:47.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.29,0:58:10.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你介意吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.47,0:58:12.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不介意\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.10,0:58:33.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么?  - 韩语 我来开车\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- What's that?  - Korean, I'm going to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.96,0:58:36.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿! 嘿! 嘿! 不! 不! 不! 这是警车!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey! Hey! Hey! No! No! No! This is a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:39.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么做! 不 不能这样 女士\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You can't! No, this is not possible, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:41.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这是警车!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.40,0:58:44.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.36,0:59:00.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 先生 很抱歉 先生\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sir, sir, excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.86,0:59:02.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I need to talk to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.36,0:59:07.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我是德国公民 我要见律师\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look, I'm a German citizen and I demand us a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.22,0:59:40.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你平时都这么开车吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do you always drive like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.77,0:59:42.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前没开过车\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I never driven before.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.73,0:59:43.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,真好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.56,0:59:52.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 这是单行道!  - 我们要迟到了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Hey, this is one way!  - We're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.83,1:00:15.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 迟到总比没命好吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, I would rather be late than dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.52,1:00:16.98,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会死的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We never really die.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.77,1:01:09.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 先生 我不同意...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sorry, sir, I don't agree...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.55,1:01:18.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我没意见\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.53,1:01:33.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉他们别跟着我们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm going to tell them to stop following us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.04,1:01:34.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻烦了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.93,1:02:58.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,把箱子给我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Give me the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.88,1:04:09.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,打开\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.65,1:04:24.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.85,1:04:27.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我什么都帮不到你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm not sure I could be of any help for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.08,1:04:33.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你帮得到\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.21,1:04:35.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么帮?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.77,1:04:43.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,提醒我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}A reminder.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.06,1:04:45.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可以走了吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.66,1:05:14.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去哪里?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.94,1:05:16.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个路口左转\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Take the first left.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.73,1:05:19.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.06,1:05:43.29,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 教授?  - 谢谢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Professor?  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.29,1:05:44.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好?  - 我是露西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Yes?  - Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.21,1:05:46.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是她 她打来了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's her, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.77,1:05:49.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你好 你在巴黎?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey you, you're in Paris?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.46,1:05:50.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我到了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, I'm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.51,1:05:52.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 太好了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Good, good, excellant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.63,1:05:57.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我已经离开酒店了 来大学里了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, look, I'm no longer at the hotel now, uh, I've come to the university
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.42,1:06:02.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经请来几位同事一起讨论你的事情了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}where I've taken the liberty of calling and gathering a few of my colleagues to discuss your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.04,1:06:05.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是各自领域的精英... 可以信赖\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Top men in their field and um... very trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:06.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.80,1:06:10.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 谢谢 那我们可以在学校见吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, thank you. So, do you think you can meet us here at the university?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.02,1:06:18.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 我很高兴见到你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm, uh...I'm very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.45,1:06:20.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.16,1:06:22.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是德·里奥警长  - 你好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Captain Del Rio.  - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.43,1:06:27.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 介绍同事给你认识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let... let me introduce you to my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.37,1:06:29.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是卡帝亚教授 脑外科医生\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is Professor Cartier, neuro surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.84,1:06:31.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 教授...  - 所有人我都认识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Professor...  - I know who everyone is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.29,1:06:34.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 当然\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.77,1:06:39.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 先生们 这位是露西 第一个女人...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Uh, gentlemen, this is Lucy, the first woman to...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.26,1:06:42.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说... 我之前有介绍...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean... like I mentioned earlier...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.88,1:06:46.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,露西小姐 因为某种对我来说还是个迷的原因\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ms. Lucy has for reasons, remains a mystery to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.50,1:06:50.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她脑部的某些区域得到开发\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}unlocked certain portion of her brain
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.33,1:06:51.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可以进入\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}that offered access
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.88,1:06:55.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们... 未知的某些领域\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}to... previously unexplored celebral zones.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.66,1:06:59.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她有超能力\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}She has abilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.66,1:07:01.28,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,能给我们示范下吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Can you give us an example?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.37,1:07:04.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你的女儿 盖布里埃尔 六岁时死于车祸\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Your daughter, Gabriel, aged 6, died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.80,1:07:07.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是辆蓝色轿车 皮座椅...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It was a blue car, leather seats...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.16,1:07:09.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,后视镜上有只塑料小鸟挂饰\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}plastic bird hanging from the rear view mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.87,1:07:52.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,有人要来了 你能守住这里吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}There're men coming here, can you secure the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.83,1:07:55.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我需要集中注意力  - 好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I need to stay focus.  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.72,1:08:02.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Speed it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.17,1:08:14.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你如何掌握这些信息的?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}How did you manage to access all these information?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.39,1:08:16.21,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,电子脉冲...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Electrical impulses...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.22,1:08:19.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,每个细胞都熟悉其他的细胞 并且相互交流\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Every cell knows and talks to every other cell.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.30,1:08:22.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此间每秒钟交换一千比特信息\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}They exchange a thousand bits of information between them per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.63,1:08:25.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,细胞们聚在一起 形成强大的通信网\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Cells group together, forming a giant web of communication
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.24,1:08:28.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,然后构成物质\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}which in turn forms matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.01,1:08:32.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,细胞们聚在一起 组成形态\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Cells get together, take on one form,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.54,1:08:34.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,变形 再重新组合\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}deform, reform,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.55,1:08:36.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,本质上没什么不同 都是一样的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}makes no difference, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.55,1:08:39.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,人类认为自己独一无二\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Human considers themself unique.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.48,1:08:43.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们将人类存在的所有理论都植根于独特上\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, they rooted their whole theory of existence on their uniqueness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.19,1:08:46.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,"一"... 是衡量一切的标准 但其实不是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}"One"... is the unit of measure but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:49.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的社交系统不过只是"草图"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}All social systems we put into place are mere "sketch".
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.54,1:08:52.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一加一等于二 这是我们唯一知道的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}1 + 1 = 2 That's all we learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.30,1:08:55.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但一加一从来就不等于二\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But 1 + 1 has never equalled 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.50,1:08:58.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 没有所谓的数字或字母\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}They're in fact, no numbers and no letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:02.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把自己的存在用人类的概念去解释\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We codify our existence to bring it down to human size
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.06,1:09:04.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,以便理解\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}to make it comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.11,1:09:09.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们创造了尺度 忘记其实一切变幻莫测\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We created the scale so that we can forget its unfathomable scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.33,1:09:14.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果人类不是衡量的标尺\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But if humans are not the unit of measure,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.06,1:09:17.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,世界也不是由数学原理掌控的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the world isn't governed by mathemathical laws,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.02,1:09:20.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来掌控一切?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}what governs all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.36,1:09:24.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆车驶过路面...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Form a car speeding down the road...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.56,1:09:27.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,加速这幅画面无穷快\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}speed up the image infinitely
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.89,1:09:29.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,车辆消失\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the car disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.54,1:09:35.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 什么证明了我们的存在?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, what proof do we have of its existence?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.81,1:09:38.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,时间给我们存在合法性\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Time gives legitimacy to its existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.15,1:09:41.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,时间是衡量一切的标准\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Time is the only true unit of meassure.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.74,1:09:44.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,它证明物质的存在\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It gives proof to the existence of matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.00,1:09:46.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Without time,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.53,1:09:49.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不存在\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}we don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.43,1:09:57.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,时间才是"个体"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Time is "unity".
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:13.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们撑不了太久的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We wouldn't be able to hold them for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.49,1:10:16.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那开始吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Time to go then.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.19,1:10:32.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定要这么大剂量?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Are you sure you need such huge doses?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.24,1:10:33.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕你承受不了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm afraid you won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.72,1:10:37.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我身体里的一些细胞会誓死捍卫它们的完整性\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Some cells inside me will fight and defend their integrity to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.91,1:10:41.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,为了开发最后一部分 我必须逼迫它们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}In order to attain the last few percent, I've to force it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.72,1:10:44.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,击破细胞 打开细胞核\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To crack the cells open to their nucleus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.35,1:10:55.28,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这些知识 露西...\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}All these knowledge, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.33,1:11:00.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不确定人类能否接受\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm not even sure that mankind is ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.32,1:11:02.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被权势利益所驱使\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're so driven by power and profit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.33,1:11:05.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于人类本性\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Given man's nature,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.40,1:11:09.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这只会给我们带来动荡和混乱\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}it might bring us only instability and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.86,1:11:16.29,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,无知才导致混乱 不是知识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ignorance brings chaos, not knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.44,1:11:19.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我会造一个电脑 把我所知的一切放在里面\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll build a computer and download all my knowledge in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.76,1:11:22.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我会想办法把它给你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll find a way for you to have access to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.29,1:11:24.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.95,1:11:28.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你的牺牲是值得的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I just hope, we'll be worthy of your sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.68,1:11:39.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不准动!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.23,1:11:59.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,能听懂英语吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do you understand English?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.33,1:13:02.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她在干吗?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.66,1:13:05.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她在寻找能量和物质\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}She's looking for energy and matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.37,1:13:12.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,还在尝试连接我们的电脑\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And she's trying to connect with our computers.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.93,1:14:17.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 怎么回事?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh my God, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.49,1:14:30.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什么?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's she making?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.37,1:14:32.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是新一代的计算机\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}A new generation of computer, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.49,1:21:04.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 说你呢!\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.39,1:21:23.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,看电脑 它在移动\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look, the computer, it's moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.29,1:21:51.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:53.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪里了?\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.61,1:22:25.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,十亿年前 我们被赐予了生命\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Life was given to us a billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.03,1:22:28.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你知道能用它做什么了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now you know what to do with it.
